data.description:
EXCEPTIONALLY MAINTAINED ARLINGTON HOME!!! Love and personalization are evident throughout, with features light white oak hardwood flooring, a fully upgraded kitchen in '22 with custom cabinets and gold stainless steel handles, and a stylish bathroom renovation. The HVAC system, baseboards, paint, and window blinds were all replaced in '22.
The entrance showcases a unique white wood wall, and the master bedroom boasts an impressive hickory wood wall. Located in a prime spot with convenient access to shops, schools, parks, and more. Act fast—THIS RARE GEM WON'T LAST!!!
